though.

265
00:10:20.828 --> 00:10:22.872
You're not going
to say what group it was?

266
00:10:22.913 --> 00:10:24.332
You don't want
to say what-- which group?

267
00:10:24.373 --> 00:10:26.042
It was the group
that was supposed to--

268
