it was supposed to be
a mind experiment.

269
00:10:28.294 --> 00:10:30.254
-Huh?
-Whoever came to your mind.

270
00:10:30.338 --> 00:10:31.881
But it was a joke.
It doesn't matter.

271
00:10:31.964 --> 00:10:34.133
