-Just say the group. dude.

272
00:10:34.216 --> 00:10:35.384
Just say what the group is.

273
00:10:35.426 --> 00:10:36.552
Sorry. I'm with Charlie here.

274
00:10:36.636 --> 00:10:38.262
and I don't-- we don't even
know who you are.

275
00:10:38.346 --> 00:10:39.889
Who are you?

276
00:10:39.930 --> 00:10:41.891
How did you get in here?
This is a private event.

277
